[The etiology and, indeed most probably, etiologies of the FUO (fever of unknown origin), or PIE (pyrexia of indeterminate etiology), illnesses is/are likely to be multi-factorial, including viral infections such as dengue and chikungunya, rickettsial diseases such as scrub typhus, as well as lots of other infections and even non-infectious diseases. - Mod.LL

